# Optional: teams handling highly sensitive content can opt-out of tracking
# captured lessons and synthesis by uncommenting the lines below. The default
# is to VERSION-CONTROL captures so the team's accumulated lessons are shared;
# the pre-commit PII hook is the primary defense against leaking sensitive data.
# history/lessons-learned/
# history/synthesis/
